OL,6,FEaster eggs have gone up in price by
OL,7,Fas much as 50% on last year while
OL,8,Fshrinking in size, according to an
OL,9,Finvestigation.
OL,11,FThe price of chocolate has risen by
OL,12,F16.5% in a year ` compared to a 4.4%
OL,13,Fincrease for supermarket food and
OL,14,Fdrink overall ` according to inflation
OL,15,Ftracking by Which?.
OL,17,FIt comes after a steep fall in global
OL,18,Fcocoa production, driven by higher
OL,19,Ftemperatures hindering the quality and
OL,20,Fquantity of beans, started driving
OL,21,Fwholesale costs to record highs.
