OL,6,FAn 80g pouch of Terry's chocolate
OL,7,Forange mini eggs at Lidl cost 99p in
OL,8,Fthe run up to Easter in 2024 but has
OL,9,Fgone up to #1.35 while shrinking to
OL,10,F70g ` meaning a price rise of 56% per
OL,11,F100g.
OL,13,FThe same product, which originally
OL,14,Fcost more at other supermarkets, has
OL,15,Fgone up by 51% at Asda, 37% at
OL,16,FSainsbury's and 14% at Tesco.
